properties.headline: Small Craft Advisory issued January 6 at 3:17PM CST until January 8 at 4:00AM CST by NWS Milwaukee/Sullivan WI
properties.description:
...Gusty Winds Expected Tuesday into Tuesday Evening...

.Gusty west winds are expected after a cold front moves through
the area during the day on Tuesday. These winds will linger into
Tuesday night.

* WHAT...West to northwest winds 15 to 25 kt with gusts up to 30
kt expected.

* WHERE...Sheboygan to Winthrop Harbor IL.

* WHEN...From noon Tuesday to 4 AM CST Wednesday.

* IMPACTS...Conditions will be hazardous to small craft.
properties.instruction:
Inexperienced mariners, especially those operating smaller
vessels, should avoid navigating in hazardous conditions.

NWSheadline: SMALL CRAFT ADVISORY IN EFFECT FROM NOON TUESDAY TO 4 AM CST WEDNESDAY
